{"type":"answer","id":61850,"parentType":"question","parentId":9602,"uid":5000,"contents":"小心漏掉关键一句释义：<br>\n<ol><br>\n<li>name calling级（辱骂）：类似于“你就是个笨蛋”</li><br>\n<li>ad hominem级（诉诸人身）：<b>不针对发言内容讨论</b>，而是攻击对方的个人特质</li><br>\n<li>responding to tone级（批评语气）：<b>不针对发言内容讨论</b>，而是批评对方的语气</li><br>\n</ol><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7J5HSmR.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7J5HSmR.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7J5HSmR.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-10-14","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":1}